code: @Override protected KafkaTableSourceBase createKafkaTableSource(TableSchema schema, Optional<String> proctimeAttribute, List<RowtimeAttributeDescriptor> rowtimeAttributeDescriptors, Map<String, String> fieldMapping, String topic, Properties properties, DeserializationSchema<Row> deserializationSchema, StartupMode startupMode, Map<KafkaTopicPartition, Long> specificStartupOffsets) {     return new Kafka011TableSource(schema, proctimeAttribute, rowtimeAttributeDescriptors, Optional.of(fieldMapping), topic, properties, deserializationSchema, startupMode, specificStartupOffsets). }

@Override protected KafkaTableSinkBase createKafkaTableSink(TableSchema schema, String topic, Properties properties, Optional<FlinkKafkaPartitioner<Row>> partitioner, SerializationSchema<Row> serializationSchema) {     return new Kafka011TableSink(schema, topic, properties, partitioner, serializationSchema). }
